               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was returning from Bond-street, and in Beer-street I passed the two gentlemen—I trod on something, which I saw was a handkerchief—I stooped and picked it up—the last gentleman took me, and accused me of picking his friend's pocket—I said I picked it up.</p>
